text: Cody Harrell Horn (born June 12, 1988) is an American actress and model. She was born in Los Angeles, California. She has appeared on Rescue Me and guest starred on three episodes of The Office. She also played Lynetta Loski in the 2010 movie Flipped and starred as Michelle, in the James Wan produced horror thriller movie Demonic. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:Models from Los Angeles
